---
import Heading from '../components/heading.astro'
import Socials from '../components/socials.astro'
---

<section id='about' class='section min-h-screen'>
  <div class='flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 max-w-[50rem] element-to-animate animate-from-bottom'>
    <!-- heading -->
    <Heading title='About' />

    <div class='flex flex-col gap-10 md:gap-6'>
      <!-- about -->
      <div class='flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-24'>
        <p
          class='text-textDark leading-8 md:leading-9 text-center md:text-left order-1 md:order-none'
        >
          Hello everyone! I am a Frontend Developer specialized in building web applications with
          React. My relevant experience includes developing a web platform to promote tourism and
          culture in our region alongside other developers. This experience has taught me a lot
          about technical skills and the process of collaborating with others. For this new year, I
          am pursuing new opportunities to expand my skills, tackle new challenges, and continue to
          grow professionally while working with talented people in the tech field.
        </p>
        <img src='images/profile.jpg' alt='profile picture' class='w-64 h-64 md:mt-3 mx-auto' />
      </div>

      <!-- social icons -->
      <div class='flex gap-4 items-center mx-auto md:mx-0'>
        <p class='text-textDark'>Find me on:</p>
        <dv class='flex gap-3'><Socials /></dv>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
